remarks of President Rajoy.

00:19:04.340 --> 00:19:08.400
Mario is an example cautioning
us of the danger of falling

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:12.290
into the illusion of thinking
from the comfort of our homes,

00:19:12.290 --> 00:19:16.380
