00:59:52.530 --> 00:59:57.440
And immediately I wrote my first
play after the experiences,

00:59:57.440 --> 01:00:02.100
the strong experiences which
was for me to see this play.

01:00:02.100 --> 01:00:05.640
And then, for example, a
French writer, Flaubert,

01:00:05.640 --> 01:00:09.230
marked me very, very
much as a writer.

01:00:09.230 --> 01:00:12.930
I think I discovered the
