01:02:11.440 --> 01:02:12.740
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Mm-hmm.

01:02:12.740 --> 01:02:14.040
Absolutely.

01:02:14.040 --> 01:02:18.550
You know, in a symposium, ED
Grossman, your translator, who,

01:02:18.550 --> 01:02:20.070
