01:02:30.570 --> 01:02:31.870
&gt;&gt; Mario Vargas Llosa:
An archeologist?

01:02:31.870 --> 01:02:33.170
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: Yes.

01:02:33.170 --> 01:02:40.010
