01:07:12.450 --> 01:07:16.570
poems which were absolutely
revolutionary and perfect.

01:07:16.570 --> 01:07:21.070
And this can be very depressing if
you don't have this natural force

01:07:21.070 --> 01:07:23.650
of creativity that Rimbaud had.

01:07:23.650 --> 01:07:28.560
Well, Flaubert is much more
human because he's something

01:07:28.560 --> 01:07:37.190
that working very, very hard could
reach the kind of originality,

01:07:37.190 --> 01:07:44.210
creativity, that the natural born
genius that was Rimbaud produced.

01:07:44.210 --> 01:07:51.640 position:56%
You know? That is why I think to
read not only the novels of Flaubert

01:07:51.640 --> 01:07:55.920
but the correspondence of
Flaubert, particularly the letters

01:07:55.920 --> 01:08:03.430
