extraordinary.

01:08:08.110 --> 01:08:14.730
Because you see, reading these
letters, how he was able to build,

01:08:14.730 --> 01:08:19.080 position:56%
to construct his talent, his genius.

01:08:19.080 --> 01:08:24.470
You know? Working very, very
hard, not accepting, you know,

01:08:24.470 --> 01:08:27.400
what he has done, convinced

01:08:27.400 --> 01:08:33.280
that this could be
improved, could be perfected.

01:08:33.280 --> 01:08:37.810
You know? And I think this is
something that helped me very,

01:08:37.810 --> 01:08:40.520
very much when I was
writing my first novels.

01:08:40.520 --> 01:08:41.820
You know?

01:08:41.820 --> 01:08:43.120
&gt;&gt; Marie Arana: The
notion that you need

